澳大利亚总理[[托尼·艾伯特|托尼·艾伯特]]受邀赴现场观赛，但因{{link-en|2015年昆士兰州选举|2015 Queensland state election}}正在计票而未能前往<ref>{{cite web|title=Tony Abbott says he will not resign in wake of LNP's Queensland rout; result described as 'catastrophic' by federal MPs|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-02-01/abbott-determined-to-stay-on-as-pm/6060490|publisher=abc.net.au|accessdate=2015-02-02|archive-date=2015-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150201231454/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-02-01/abbott-determined-to-stay-on-as-pm/6060490|dead-url=no}}</ref>。艾伯特此前也曾出席在墨尔本举行的澳大利亚对阵科威特的揭幕战<ref>{{cite web|title=Live Asian Cup 2015: Australia v Kuwait|url=http://www.smh.com.au/sport/soccer/soccer-match-centre/live-asian-cup-2015-australia-v-kuwait-20150109-12l273.html|publisher=smh.com.au|accessdate=2015-02-02|archive-date=2015-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112005103/http://www.smh.com.au/sport/soccer/soccer-match-centre/live-asian-cup-2015-australia-v-kuwait-20150109-12l273.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他现场嘉宾包括[[国际足联主席|国际足联主席]][[塞普·布拉特|塞普·布拉特]]、{{link-en|亚洲足球联合会主席|List of Presidents of AFC}}{{link-en|萨勒曼·阿勒哈利法|Salman Al-Khalifa}}和[[澳大利亚足球协会|澳大利亚足球协会]]主席{{link-en|弗兰克·洛伊|Frank Lowy}}。布拉特和阿勒哈利法为冠军队颁发奖杯<ref>{{cite web|title=Australia rising in Asia, on and off the field|url=http://news.yahoo.com/australia-rising-asia-off-field-152204962.html|publisher=yahoo.com|accessdate=2015-02-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206030732/http://news.yahoo.com/australia-rising-asia-off-field-152204962.html|archivedate=2015-02-06}}</ref>。

比赛由[[澳大利亚广播公司|ABC]]和[[Fox_Sports|Fox Sports]]负责在澳大利亚的转播。ABC的转播平均有180万名观众全程收看赛事，观众总数达到530万。ABC的观众峰值时段出现在澳洲东部时间22:27，有300万名观众同时观看，是比赛中加时赛最后一分钟。Fox Sports的转播平均有416000万名观众观看<ref>{{cite web|title=Socceroos score for ABC and Foxtel|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/business/media/socceroos-score-for-abc-and-foxtel/story-e6frg996-1227204139206|accessdate=2015-02-05|archive-date=2015-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418055249/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/business/media/socceroos-score-for-abc-and-foxtel/story-e6frg996-1227204139206|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

